Package Interfaces

Interface IEntity

All Known Implementing Classes:
Admin, Appointment, AppointmentOutcome, Doctor, Inventory, Leave, MedicalRecord, Patient, Pharmacist, Prescription, Staff, User
public interface IEntity
The IEntity interface defines the contract for entity objects, specifying methods for obtaining an entity's unique identifier, converting the entity to and from CSV format, and representing it as a string.
